The Vice President of Nigeria, Professor Yemi Osinbajo praises his wife, Oludolapo, as she celebrates her birthday. Osinbajo took to his Instagram page and described his wife as his past, present and his future. He said: ” I found a girl, beautiful and sweet many years ago. I got to know you and you became Queen of my heart. You are my past, my present and my future. You complete me! You are as beautiful as the day I met you. Happy Birthday Oludolapo, your heart is my home.“